}

dev --> analyze
agent --> extract
agent --> semantic
ks --> store

analyze ..> extract : <<include>>
extract ..> store : <<include>>
semantic ..> export : <<include>>
store ..> graphdb : <<include>>
export ..> sync : <<include>>

graphdb --> writegraph
sync --> leveldb
export --> jsonread

km --> store
ukb --> semantic
mcpops --> extract

note right of store : "Stored at .data/knowledge-graph\nusing Graphology + LevelDB"
note right of export : "Auto-synced to .data/knowledge-export\nfrom GraphDB"
note bottom of analyze : "Pattern extracted from:\nsrc/knowledge-management\nlib/ukb-unified\nintegrations/mcp-server-semantic-analysis/src"

